            <title>[LU-14319] Make foreign layout as a mirror component</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14319</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A closer coupling between the HSM archive state (a kind of a foreign layout) and Lustre File Level Redundancy (FLR) can make PCC and HSM management more consistent with the management of other replicas in the file system.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This ticket tracks the basic functionality to make foreign layout as a FLR mirror component.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
